The paper focuses on collaborative filtering, which is a popular technique in machine learning and falls under the category of supervised learning. The paper also discusses distributed learning and parameter server paradigm, which are related to distributed systems and parallel computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). 

The paper also discusses the use of hashing technique for online recommendation, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and data structures (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper mentions real-world applications in Ant Financial, which suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
